create iteration

create_iteration.Rd

create iteration

create_iteration(
  name,
  start_date,
  end_date,
  description,
  config = list(),
  sc_token = get_token()
)

Arguments

name

Required. The name of this Iteration.

start_date

as character. Required. The date this Iteration begins, e.g. "2019-07-01".

end_date

as character. Required. The date this Iteration ends, e.g. "2019-07-01".

description

Required. The description of the Iteration.

config

(optional) additional configuration to add to header

sc_token

shortcut API token. Defaults to get_token()

Details

arguments for follower_ids, group_ids, labels are not yet implemented. See issue 2 to contribute.

Examples

if (FALSE) {
create_iteration(
  name = "09 Jan - 15 Jan 2022",
  description = "Sprint Q1-1 2022",
  start_date = "2022-01-09",
  end_date = "2022-01-15"
)
}
